content.rendered:
Directed by Pragati Agarwal

Written by Pragati Agarwal

Cast Romil Chaudhary (Ajay Wardhan). Priya Sharma (Pragati). Abhimanyu Aryan (jr. Ajay). Yogesh (jr. Vijay). Kshitej Singh (Elder brother). Ramandeep Yadav (Ankit bagga). Malkeet Singh (Arshdeep). Dimple Sharma (Mandira). Barkha Pundir (Ridhima). Dimple (Pragati’s mother). Girish Thapar (Father). Anuj (Vicky). Sachin Passi (Dean). Nandini Passi (Vice Principal). Tarun Kalra (Head Professor). Saurav Bakshi (Ajay’s college friend). Aishwarya Raj Bhakuni. Aman Bhogal (Ajay’s Mother). Arjumman Mughal. Ruslaan Mumtaz. Rashiprabha Sandeepani. Bhaskar Sharma (MBBS doctor)

Language Hindi

Production Prasidh Eklavaya Entertainment
